            <div class="summary-item"><span class="summary-label">Ice Level:</span><span id="summaryIceLevel" class="summary-value">-</span></div>
            <div class="summary-item"><span class="summary-label">Sugar Level:</span><span id="summarySugarLevel" class="summary-value">-</span></div>
